Second Department,

January, 1938.

(January 4, 1938.) In the Matter of the Appointment of Honorable Albert H. F. Seeger as an Official Referee.

Honorable Albert H. F. Seeger appointed an official referee to take effect as of January 1, 1938. Present — Hagarty, Carswell, Davis, Johnston, Adel, Taylor and Close, JJ.
